        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绑上山去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将那厮绑上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，蛮子绑上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了本大王为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃堂堂大将，岂来跪你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来。将他绑在剥衣厅挖心，与大王宴酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（头目上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "头目",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离了后山到前山，不觉跑的两腿酸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "头目",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甚么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "头目",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲家到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "头目",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家大王得了一骑马，请你家大王演马吃酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀大王：后山大王得了一骑马，请大王演马打狗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，演马吃酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，演马吃酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就说你家大王修帖不及，随后就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家大王修帖不及，随后就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "头目",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲家你也来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抓地虎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李刚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将这汉子绑在剥皮厅，候大王回来，挖心宴酒。带马来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李刚下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，这一汉子。我家大王到后山演马吃酒去了，你可有金银拿三五百两，我把"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你放了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有银钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十几吊钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百十个钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一文无有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "该你不得活。我的困来了，我要困，你可不要闹，闹醒我的困，我跟你算帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初在朝中何等安享，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这也是为国家自遭祸殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君臣们要相逢梦里一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保周朝坐天下万古名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这也是大祸到自遭其殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二丫鬟、班氏同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后面来了班老大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身班氏。正在上房打坐，忽听剥皮厅有人啼哭，说甚么李克昌，老身前者配"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫李克昌，乃大朝人氏，征战我国招赘，与我配婚数日，回朝交旨，至今有了"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二十馀载。所生一子，取名李刚，文武全才。当日我夫讲到，家有一子名唤李"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "广。方才听得有人言道什么李广。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟。前去问抓地虎，何人叫苦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抓地虎，抓地虎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我来诓他一诓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是谁的二百钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太夫人在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抓地虎叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。抓地虎，甚么人啼哭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王在山下擒了一汉子，绑在剥皮厅，故而啼哭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你去到后山，接大王回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王把那汉子交与我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去，交与我就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抓地虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "交与你？他走了，不与我相干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不与你相干。有我哪，你去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（抓地虎下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，问那汉子家住哪里，姓甚名谁？讲个明白，放他下山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！这一汉子，我家大王问你，家住哪里，姓甚名谁？讲个明白，放你下山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫你那强盗婆，打坐上前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "强盗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是强盗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请太夫人打坐上前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一汉子，家住哪里，姓甚名谁？说明白，放你下山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未曾开言泪先淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊一声大王听详情："
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "里城之内有家门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李广就是我的名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家住大国天胆地"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的父名叫李克昌"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来心内惊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来姣儿到山林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姣儿不住口内称。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走上前来忙松捆"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山岗之上迷了性，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人称娘亲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姣儿有所不知情，"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你父与我配为婚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说此话我不信，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何物件作证明？"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿若还不肯信，"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现有宝剑作证凭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“李克昌”……啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见宝剑泪珠滚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想起当年大事情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日相逢在山林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲在上，孩儿拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走上前来双膝跪"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。一旁坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿告坐。母亲，那一黑汉，他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那就是你李刚兄弟。你不在朝中奉君，为何来到此地？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因为谗臣当道，孩儿保定国母，天涯逃生，被猛虎冲散，又被兄弟拿住。啊母"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲，不知兄弟往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被后山大王请去赴席去了。后堂摆宴，与我儿压惊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "班氏",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母子今见面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骨肉又团圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
